===Noun===
'''litre'''  {{UK}}

# The [[metric]] [[unit]] of [[fluid measure]]; one [[cubic]] [[decimetre]].  Symbols: l, L, &#x2113; (''Notes: the litre is not an SI unit but is accepted for use with SI units.  The official SI symbols are the capital'' L ''or lower-case roman'' l.  ''The script symbol'' &#x2113;, ''while not officially sanctioned, was sometimes used in non-technical contexts to prevent the lower-case roman'' l ''being confused with the number 1 (one).'')

